矯視lasik或smile 分享下<br />\n<br />\n黎緊會去香矯做激光，想問下各位意見做lasik好定smile</blockquote><br />\n香矯你搵邊個醫生?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSor 巴打，覆遲左，冇搵指定醫生，會有唔同？"},{"pid":"b26a5c143a38aa6cb2d25a65ce45d151c33b570a","tid":17263,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T00:54:55.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d9b465752e4e63dcf696c030e1deb75a5fd9d3cf","tid":17263,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T09:50:04.000Z","msg":"左聽talk...<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lnzq2txh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flnzq2txh&h=fc0e65c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e583c363dba5c6539342352b5fdcfead6cd9e0df","tid":17263,"uid":50538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>左聽talk...<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lnzq2txh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flnzq2txh&h=fc0e65c1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地點講？？？？？"},{"pid":"0df72347872dfd53385d56677be1be52a7f221a5","tid":17263,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>左聽talk...<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lnzq2txh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flnzq2txh&h=fc0e65c1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地點講？？？？？</blockquote><br />\n都係啲行野， 介紹PRK, LASIK, SMILE, 都係講到SMILE好啲咁， 但係個講師佢話佢唔做激光係因為佢份工係做矯視， 有家庭， 承擔唔起後果， 但係話有90%人有完美視力，全球有6萬人做過SMILE, 全港有3千人度。"},{"pid":"1e38e285454ffb7c7e9a46e1a1c968d256f42dae","tid":17263,"uid":49716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:34:21.000Z","msg":"我11月做左lasik 暫時一切良好，視力正常，只係有時會眼乾，keep住滴下眼藥水就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但唯一既後遺症我覺得係夜晚望燈會化開咁，如果你成日夜晚要揸車你可能要諗諗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058550a0af9cc49765c10c380d4161ac316b4bca","tid":17263,"uid":63244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:38:04.000Z","msg":"2014年4月做左一次lasik@養和<br />\n2015年3月補做一隻眼清埋個100度散光<br />\n到而家無補做個隻眼一直keep住50度散光 另一隻零度數<br />\n兩次都無不適 眼乾都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}